<L>__{exterior hair salon evening.}
<A>__{fergus emerges from the shop. he takes one last look through the window where dil is taking off her smock, touching up her hair, etc. it is as if she has forgotten all about him. he walks off through the crowds and then ducks into a doorway. the doorway of the shop. dil comes out, dressed in a pair of high heels, a very short skirt, different, more raunchy clothes on her than we saw inside. she locks the glass door and walks down the street, across the road, and into a pub called the metro. fergus follows.}
